   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>MH 143, recto: (1) Pamonthes, son of Totoes, son of Pamonthes, has paid (2) to the bank of the northern houses for silver of poll (3) of year 4 in Jeme, 2 staters / 1 stater / 2 staters again. (4) Written in year 4 of Tiberius, Epiphi (5) 20. Likewise, on the 29th, 2 staters / (6) 1 stater / 2 staters again. Likewise, on Mesore (7) 16, for the bath (tax), 1 kite.</ab>
